  "text": "An additional aim of the investigation was to assess the neural substrates of abnormalities in action competition. We conducted support-vector regression lesion symptom mapping analyses to assess the prediction that a core set of regions, including the left SMG and IFG, would be associated both with reduced competition on the Stroop-like task and poor performance with 'conflict' tools [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] .",
